"@Consumes(MediaType.TEXT_PLAIN)\n"
"public class QuarkusKmsSyncResource {\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/amazon-kms.adoc:137
#, no-wrap
